descript.abstract: This point data layer represents addresses for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Addresses_2015.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: This data was downloaded on September 8, 2015 from ArcGIS Online. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable.
